<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>SINGLE SPEED REAR AXLE: INTERNATIONAL - CLEAN AND INSPECT - INSPECT</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="6">
        <title>INSPECT</title>
        <para>Prior to reassembly, inspect parts for signs of excessive wear or damage. Replacement of these parts can
            prevent premature failure and costly downtime.
        </para>
        <para>Bearing surfaces should be inspected for pitting, excessive wear, or overheating (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1400824">Figure 24</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f1400824" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1400824" filename="../figg14/G1400824.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 24. Bearings</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Inspect thrust washers for scoring or cracking (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1400825">Figure 25</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f1400825" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1400825" filename="../figg14/G1400825.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 25. Thrust Washers</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Inspect gears for wear or damage. Replace gears that are pitted, scored, broken or worn (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1400826">Figure 26</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f1400826" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1400826" filename="../figg14/G1400826.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 26. Gears</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Inspect shafts for nicks or scores (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1400827">Figure 27</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f1400827" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1400827" filename="../figg14/G1400827.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 27. Shafts</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Inspect all splines for wear, distortion from twisting, and cracking (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1400828">Figure 28</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f1400828" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1400828" filename="../figg14/G1400828.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 28. Splines</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Inspect housing for stripped threads and bending fatigue (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1400829">Figure 29</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f1400829" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1400829" filename="../figg14/G1400829.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 29. Housings</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
